    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Deadly Chance</i>, you are forced to confront the terror of a house filled with mysteries and unspeakable horrors. With each step, you become further entangled in a nightmare where pain and fear intertwine, pushing your psychological and physical limits. In a dark environment full of secrets beyond human comprehension, every decision could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your only chance of survival is to unravel the mysteries surrounding your captivity and uncover the truth behind your torment. But beware: in the darkness, only the sharpest minds have any hope of escape. Every corner hides a threat, and fear becomes more than just an emotion—it’s a constant battle for survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Horror Atmosphere:</strong> Explore a dark house filled with horrors, where every corner holds something unexpected. Fear and tension are tangible every second.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/61ebff7f2e4b09b6743c4523a9a0a822.poster.avif?t=1749502484\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/61ebff7f2e4b09b6743c4523a9a0a822.webm?t=1749502484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/61ebff7f2e4b09b6743c4523a9a0a822.mp4?t=1749502484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choices with Consequences:</strong> Your decisions shape the story. Each choice could be your last and directly impact your chances of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/b96ce51458b024a7da194e5e40b377ef.poster.avif?t=1749502484\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/b96ce51458b024a7da194e5e40b377ef.webm?t=1749502484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/b96ce51458b024a7da194e5e40b377ef.mp4?t=1749502484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense and Emotional Narrative:</strong> Uncover the truth behind your captivity as you navigate dark secrets and face relentless challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/73f5d14107a835fb44a52184fd3007d4.poster.avif?t=1749502484\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/73f5d14107a835fb44a52184fd3007d4.webm?t=1749502484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334220/extras/73f5d14107a835fb44a52184fd3007d4.mp4?t=1749502484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
